(2, 1, '2016-11-07 10:16:34', '2016-11-07 10:16:34', '[vc_row][vc_column][about_section_hero_header title1=\"Not Just Forward-Thinking—Future-Thinking.\"]At Revature, we don\'t just see the future of business and technology—we\'re creating it[/about_section_hero_header][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][about_sub_nav][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][about_advance_and_tech_func main_title=\"Advancing Talent and Technologies.\" main_content=\"Revature empowers businesses around the globe with best-in-class talent and technologies. Our people work on the most innovative, challenging, and rewarding software development projects for leading Fortune 500 companies, government organizations, and top systems integrators. We offer three distinct advantages that help put our clients—and our people—ahead in the market: a one-of-a-kind talent delivery program, unparalleled expertise, and better control of your talent pipeline.\" left_img_1=\"202\" right_title_1=\"Proprietary Talent Delivery Program\" right_content_1=\"Our unique training program lets us hire, develop, and deploy top talent well versed in leading-edge and next-gen technologies. Through continuous and intensive training focused on simulated, real-world issues, Revature associates are able to quickly integrate into your existing technology teams.\" right_img_2=\"207\" left_title_2=\"Next-Gen Technologies Expertise\" left_content_2=\"We bring deep knowledge of and experience in all the latest enterprise-level technologies—and we’re constantly refining our program to incorporate the latest technology trends and enhancements in project delivery, including DevOps, SDET, and Cloud computing.\" left_img_3=\"205\" right_title_3=\"Better Control of Your Talent Pipeline\" right_content_3=\"Because our talent delivery program can train people faster and more cost-effectively, we can help you ramp up quickly and integrate expert teams in large numbers right away.\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][princi