(5, 1, '2016-11-07 12:33:46', '2016-11-07 12:33:46', '[vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_header logo_img=\"239\" header_title=\"We get IT going.\" button_text_left=\"CONTACT AN ADVISOR\" button_url_left=\"../contact-us\" button_text_right=\"APPLY NOW\" button_url_right=\"#apply\"]Don’t just move forward in technology—sprint ahead. Our breakthrough training platform, RevaturePro, gives you the advantage, working on the latest leading-edge technologies that put you at the forefront of talent in the tech industry.[/revaturepro_header][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_sub_nav_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_benefits_blue_header title=\"Move Ahead Faster.\"]RevaturePro not only gets you up to speed on the programming skills today’s industries require, it puts you miles ahead of the pack.[/revaturepro_benefits_blue_header][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_benefits_blue_items icon_1=\"216\" title_1=\"Work with relevant technologies\" content_1=\"You work intensively with enterprise-level technologies that companies are using today—as well as next-gen and niche technologies that are shaping the future of business.\" icon_2=\"217\" title_2=\"Gain real-world experience\" content_2=\"You receive valuable industry experience by working on real-world projects so that you’re truly “job-ready.”\" icon_3=\"218\" title_3=\"Learn from the best\" content_3=\"You’re guided and mentored by highly skilled professionals representing some of the top talent in technology, who not only teach you industry best practices but the “soft skills” that set you up for ultimate success.\" icon_4=\"219\" title_4=\"Showcase your talents\" content_4=\"You can develop a comprehensive online portfolio that showcases your projects, skills, experience, certifications, academic coursework, and more—equating them to actual industry experience.\" icon_5=\"220\" title_5=\"Tailor your program to your needs\" content_5=\"You can choose your technology path from a broad range of offerings, as well as learn and work on projects from anywhere.\" icon_6=\"221\" title_6=\"Start your technology career faster\" content_6=\"Our intensive program gives you the leading-edge, enterprise-level technology skills businesses need in as little as 12 weeks. Best of all, when you successfully complete the program, we’ll hire you as a Revature software development professional!\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_quick_facts title=\"Get Hired Faster. Way Faster.\" title_1=\"600+\" content_1=\"Revature professionals hired in 2015.\" title_2=\"$0\" content_2=\"Your cost to be in our program. It\'s 100% free to accepted participants!\" title_3=\"300+\" content_3=\"Enterprise technology offerings to choose from at RevaturePro.\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_testimonial title=\"What Students Are Saying About Us.\" content_1=\"I know I wouldn\'t have gotten this position if it hadn\'t been for Revature.\" name_1=\"Yasmine Sadid\" school_1=\"Kent State University (now working at Capital One)\" content_2=\"Revature truly has been in a once in a lifetime opportunity. During my time here I have been learning the stack from front to back, particularly in Java as well as automation frameworks like Cucumber which I have no doubt will prove invaluable at any company.\" name_2=\"Braden Ripple\" school_2=\"Utah State (now working as a software engineer for Walmart)\" content_3=\"The industry is evolving quickly and my biggest fear was I wasn’t going to be able to get a job. Revature came through…all I needed was that one job.\" name_3=\"Christopher Kurz\" school_3=\"B.A. in English from UCLA\" content_4=\"We work on cool stuff. College was great but the curriculum was set in stone, Revature teaches you the newer technologies such as Hibernate.\" name_4=\"Kevin Jones\" school_4=\"Oregon State\" content_5=\"If I hadn’t done this program, I think I would still be searching for a development job or possibly changing my career field. I have come here to perfect this knowledge, this technology and I’ve done it!\" name_5=\"RaVaughn Green\" school_5=\"University of Maryland\" content_6=\"The program has been amazing in taking me from a non-Computer Science background to a marketable IT professional.\" name_6=\"Omari Maxwell\" school_6=\"University of Pennsylania\" content_7=\"Part of the programming is learning how to interview and talk with people, which is challenging for most computer programmers. Revature provides a place to learn how to speak with technologists and create a rapport.\" name_7=\"Frank Emmert\" school_7=\"Purdue University\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_six_steps title_1=\"How It Works.\" content_1=\"RevaturePro’s one-of-a-kind program is available online or in-person at one of our coding bootcamps. Designed in close collaboration with our academic and corporate partners, our program delivers maximum value to participants, learning institutions, and today’s enterprises as efficiently and cost effectively as possible.\" title_2=\"Sign Up Fast & Easy\" content_2=\"Fill out an online registration form, take a quick basic skills test, and select a technical track—all in 15 minutes or less.\" img_2=\"225\" title_3=\"Start Working\" content_3=\"Whether online or in one of our bootcamps, you jump into real-world project scenarios right away, learning as you go through tutorials and mentor guidance.\" img_3=\"224\" title_4=\"Connect with a Mentor\" content_4=\"Mentorship is unique to the RevaturePro experience, both online and in our bootcamps. You’ll receive one-on-one guidance and instruction with an industry-experienced mentor throughout your program.\" img_4=\"227\" title_5=\"Get Certified\" content_5=\"Earn certifications during and upon completion of your program that highlight not only your technical abilities, but your work/project experience.\" img_5=\"228\" title_6=\"Show Off Your Skills\" content_6=\"Build an online portfolio that showcases every element of your program: skills, projects, application screenshots, sample code, certifications, ratings, and reviews.\" img_6=\"229\" title_7=\"Get Hired\" content_7=\"Start working for Revature as a software development professional, working on innovative and leading-edge projects for one of our many corporate partners.\" img_7=\"230\" id=\"howItWorks\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_two_column_container][revaturepro_two_column_header title=\"Two Ways to Move Ahead.\"]RevaturePro gives you two routes to the front of the technology talent market—online and in person. Either way, we put you in a position to win.[/revaturepro_two_column_header][revaturepro_two_column_img_left img=\"204\" title=\"Online Program\" btn_txt=\"GO TO REVATUREPRO ONLINE\" btn_url=\"../online\"]Learn leading-edge programming skills, access tutorials, and work on enterprise-level projects from anywhere, anytime.[/revaturepro_two_column_img_left][revaturepro_two_column_img_right img=\"232\" title=\"Coding Bootcamp\" btn_txt=\"GO TO REVATUREPRO BOOTCAMP\" btn_url=\"coding-bootcamp\"]Get accepted into our intensive, on-site coding bootcamp and work on leading-edge technology projects in a team-focused setting.[/revaturepro_two_column_img_right][/revaturepro_two_column_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_get_it_going title=\"Ready to Get IT Going with RevaturePro?\" btn_txt_1=\"SIGN UP FOR ONLINE TRAINING\" btn_url_1=\"https://app.revature.com/signup\" btn_txt_2=\"APPLY TO OUR BOOTCAMP\" btn_url_2=\"../bootcamp#apply\"]See how we can fast-track your technology career.[/revaturepro_get_it_going][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_faq_container title=\"Still Have Questions? We\'ve Got Answers!\" sub_title=\"Have a Specific Question?\" btn_txt=\"CONTACT US\" btn_url=\"../contact-us\"][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"What makes Revature unique?\"]Revature’s proprietary training and talent delivery platform makes us unique in the industry. Our platform ensures that the talent we provide has the job-ready, enterprise-level skills in leading-edge and niche technologies that today’s companies need right now.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"What programs does Revature offer?\"]Revature offers both an online program and an in-person coding bootcamp program. There are no qualifications necessary to enroll in the online program—just a can-do attitude and a desire to great work in the technology sector. Applicants to our coding bootcamps are required to take a skills test and undergo a short interview. Both programs are free to applicants.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Can I contact a recruiter directly about employment opportunities?\"]Yes. You can reach a recruiter directly by calling the recruitment team’s number at (703) 570-8282.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Should I apply for the online program or the residential coding bootcamp?\"]It depends. Anyone can apply to our online program—and it offers the ability to gain the skills and certifications you need from practically anywhere. However, if you already have some coding experience and wish to gain job-ready skills and certifications—as well as a guaranteed job in technology once you’ve successfully completed the program—then we suggest you apply to our coding bootcamp.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Can I join the coding bootcamp if I have no coding experience?\"]While anyone can apply, the coding bootcamp is very immersive and intensive. A background in coding is essential to successfully completing the program. If you have no coding experience, we suggest you enroll in our free online program first. Once you’ve completed that, we’d love to have you apply for one of our coding bootcamps.[/revaturepro_faq_item][/revaturepro_faq_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_two_column_callout title=\"RevaturePro for Academic Institutions\" btn_txt=\"LEARN MORE\" btn_url=\"../academic-partners\"]Learn how we can help you provide no-risk pathways to careers in technology for your students and graduates.[/revaturepro_two_column_callout][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_faq_container][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"as\"]asd[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"amar\"]amar singh[/revaturepro_faq_item][/revaturepro_faq_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Revaturepro', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'revaturepro', '', '', '2016-12-13 11:35:48', '2016-12-13 11:35:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/rough/?page_id=5', 0, 'page', '', 0),
