(22, 1, '2016-11-10 12:51:53', '2016-11-10 12:51:53', '[vc_row][vc_column][academicpartners_header title=\"Academic Partnerships\"]Empower your students with enterprise-level skills and real-world training at no additional cost. Join our growing network of partner colleges and universities to stay on the cutting edge.[/academicpartners_header][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][online_log_in_banner btn_url=\"contactus.html?academic\" btn_txt=\"LEARN MORE\"]Find out how our program can help your students land at leading Fortune 500 enterprises and government organizations.[/online_log_in_banner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][online_two_column_txt_img title=\"Closing the Gap Between College and Career.\" img_url=\"209\"]Revature is the most accessible, affordable, and inclusive talent development solution, providing a highly desirable and diverse talent pool to support the fast-evolving needs of leading companies in the tech sector.\n\nFor our university partners, Revature offers a no-risk pathway to high-demand careers in technology for all students and graduates. We help bridge the gap by providing in-demand, industry-aligned skills at no cost to you or your students, leading up to a guaranteed job in the tech industry.\n\nWith Revature’s talent development model, your students gain hands-on experience in enterprise-level, next-gen, and niche technologies. And we’re not just talking about students seeking a master’s in computer science—with our program, hundreds of students with no STEM background whatsoever have gone on to become successful software engineers.[/online_two_column_txt_img][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][academicpartners_quickfacts title_1=\"Fast-Tracking Careers in Technology.\" content_1=\"We’ll help your students gain the skills, tools, and connections to get not just a job but a fulfilling career. While you help them earn a bachelor’s or master’s degree in computer science or another major, we’ll provide real-world experience in next-gen technologies.\" title_2=\"Job-Ready Skills\" content_2=\"Your students receive valuable industry experience by working on real-world projects so that they can hit the ground running upon graduation.\" title_3=\"Guaranteed Hire\" content_3=\"Revature hires all graduates who successfully complete our bootcamp—another way we help bridge the gap between college and career.\" title_4=\"Fortune 500 Enterprises\" content_4=\"Our graduates are employed by highly desirable companies, such as Fortune 500 enterprises, government organizations, and top systems integrators.\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][academicpartners_five_steps main_title=\"Why Partner With Revature?\" main_content=\"Our program is designed to help send your students on a path to success. As our academic partner, you will benefit from full management and operational support, dedicated enrollment advisors and industry mentors, as well as marketing support and enterprise access to our RevaturePro online platform. We can also work with you to gain priority placement at our regional bootcamps or create a free on-campus bootcamp for your university.\" title_1=\"No Cost\" content_1=\"All of our online programs, coding bootcamps, and services are completely free to our university partners as well as their students and alumni—you don’t need to make any financial investment whatsoever.\" img_1=\"210\" title_2=\"No Risk\" content_2=\"As the leading-edge provider of talent development in the tech industry, Revature will put your students on a no-risk pathway to a rewarding career.\" img_2=\"211\" title_3=\"Any Major\" content_3=\"Our engaging online program provides training to students at all levels—from sophomores to seniors, non-STEM majors to those with a master’s degree in computer science.\" img_3=\"212\" title_4=\"Certifications\" content_4=\"Students can earn certifications during and upon completion of our program that highlight work experience in addition to technical abilities.\" img_4=\"213\" title_5=\"Employment\" content_5=\"We hire every student who successfully completes our immersive, industry-aligned coding bootcamp as a Revature Software Development Professional.\" img_5=\"214\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][academicpartners_for_business title=\"Become a Partner Today.\" button_text=\"INQUIRE TODAY\" button_url=\"contactus.html?academic\"]Let’s discuss how we can help you expand access to high-demand tech careers for all your students. And ask us about priority placement in our regional bootcamps or how to offer a free bootcamp on your campus.[/academicpartners_for_business][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][academicpartners_for_students title=\"RevaturePro for Students\" link_text=\"LEARN MORE\" link_url=\"revaturepro.html\"]Learn how you can fast-track your career and work on some of the most innovative, challenging, and rewarding technology for leading companies.[/academicpartners_for_students][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_advance title=\"Ready to Advance?\" button_text=\"CONTACT US\" button_url=\"contactus.html?academic\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Academic Partners', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'academic-partners', '', '', '2016-12-05 14:27:44', '2016-12-05 14:27:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/rough/?page_id=22', 0, 'page', '', 0),
