(167, 1, '2016-11-17 14:59:26', '2016-11-17 14:59:26', '[vc_row][vc_column][pro_header logo_img=\"76\" header_title=\"We get IT going.\" button_text_left=\"CONTACT AN ADVISOR\" button_url_left=\"contactus.html\" button_text_right=\"APPLY NOW\" button_url_right=\"\" bg_img=\"82\"]Don’t just move forward in technology—sprint ahead. Our breakthrough training platform, RevaturePro, gives you the advantage, working on the latest leading-edge technologies that put you at the forefront of talent in the tech industry.[/pro_header][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][about_sub_nav][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][pro_move_ahead title=\"Move Ahead Faster.\"]RevaturePro not only gets you up to speed on the programming skills today’s industries require, it puts you miles ahead of the pack.[/pro_move_ahead][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][pro_six_box content_1=\" You work intensively with enterprise-level technologies that companies are using today—as well as next-gen and niche technologies that are shaping the future of business.\" title_3=\"Learn from the best\" icon_img_1=\"88\" title_1=\"Work with relevant technologies\" title_2=\"Gain real-world experience\" content_2=\"You receive valuable industry experience by working on real-world projects so that you’re truly “job-ready.”\" icon_img_2=\"102\" icon_img_3=\"90\" content_3=\"You’re guided and mentored by highly skilled professionals representing some of the top talent in technology, who not only teach you industry best practices but the “soft skills” that set you up for ultimate success.\" icon_img_4=\"91\" title_4=\"Showcase your talents\" content_4=\"You can develop a comprehensive online portfolio that showcases your projects, skills, experience, certifications, academic coursework, and more—equating them to actual industry experience.\" icon_img_5=\"92\" title_5=\"Tailor your program to your needs\" content_5=\"You can choose your technology path from a broad range of offerings, as well as learn and work on projects from anywhere.\" icon_img_6=\"93\" title_6=\"Start your technology career faster\" content_6=\"Our intensive program gives you the leading-edge, enterprise-level technology skills businesses need in as little as 12 weeks. Best of all, when you successfully complete the program, we’ll hire you as a Revature software development professional!\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][vc_row][vc_column][pro_quick_facts title=\"Get Hired Faster. Way Faster.\" title_1=\"600+\" content_1=\"Revature professionals hired in 2015.\" title_2=\"$0\" content_2=\"Your cost to be in our program. It\'s 100% free to accepted participants!\" title_3=\"300+\" content_3=\"Enterprise technology offerings to choose from at RevaturePro.\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_testimonial school_1=\"Kent State University (now working at Capital One)\" content_2=\"Revature truly has been in a once in a lifetime opportunity. During my time here I have been learning the stack from front to back, particularly in Java as well as automation frameworks like Cucumber which I have no doubt will prove invaluable at any company.\n\" title=\"What Students Are Saying About Us.\" name_1=\"YASMINE SADID\" name_2=\" BRADEN RIPPLE\" content_1=\"I know I wouldn\'t have gotten this position if it hadn\'t been for Revature\n\" school_2=\"Utah State\" content_3=\"The industry is evolving quickly and my biggest fear was I wasn’t going to be able to get a job. Revature came through…all I needed was that one job.\n\" name_3=\"CHRISTOPHER KURZ\" school_3=\"B.A. in English from UCLA\" content_4=\"We work on cool stuff. School was great but the curriculum was set in stone, Revature teaches you the newer technologies such as Hibernate.\n\" name_4=\"KEVIN JONES\" school_4=\"Oregon State\" content_5=\"If I hadn’t done this program, I think I would still be searching for a development job or possibly changing my career field. I have come here to perfect this knowledge, this technology and I’ve done it!\n\" name_5=\"RAVAUGHN GREEN\" school_5=\"University of Maryland\" content_6=\"The program has been amazing in taking me from a non-Computer Science background to a marketable IT professional.\n\" name_6=\"OMARI MAXWELL\" school_6=\"University of Pennsylvania\" content_7=\"Part of the programming is learning how to interview and talk with people, which is challenging for most computer programmers. Revature provides a place to learn how to speak with technologists and create a report.\n\" name_7=\"FRANK EMMERT\" school_7=\"Purdue University\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][pro_six_steps main_title=\"How RevaturePro Works\" main_content=\"RevaturePro’s one-of-a-kind program is available online or in-person at one of our coding bootcamps. Designed in close collaboration with our academic and corporate partners, our program delivers maximum value to participants, learning institutions, and today’s enterprises as efficiently and cost effectively as possible.\" left_img_1=\"108\" right_title_1=\"Sign Up Fast & Easy\" right_content_1=\"Fill out an online registration form, take a quick basic skills test, and select a technical track—all in 15 minutes or less.\" right_img_2=\"109\" left_title_2=\"Start Working\" left_content_2=\"Whether online or in one of our bootcamps, you jump into real-world project scenarios right away, learning as you go through tutorials and mentor guidance.\" left_img_3=\"110\" right_title_3=\"Connect with a Mentor\" right_content_3=\"Mentorship is unique to the RevaturePro experience, both online and in our bootcamps. You’ll receive one-on-one guidance and instruction with an industry-experienced mentor throughout your program.\n\" right_img_4=\"112\" left_title_4=\"Get Certified\" left_content_4=\"Earn certifications during and upon completion of your program that highlight not only your technical abilities, but your work/project experience.\" left_img_5=\"114\" right_title_5=\"Show Off Your Skills\" right_content_5=\"Build an online portfolio that showcases every element of your program: skills, projects, application screenshots, sample code, certifications, ratings, and reviews.\" right_img_6=\"115\" left_title_6=\"Get Hired\" left_content_6=\"Start working for Revature as a software development professional, working on innovative and leading-edge projects for one of our many corporate partners.\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_img_txt_container][home_img_left_text_right title_img_left=\"Online Program\" logo_img_img_left=\"118\" button_text_img_left=\"GO TO REVATUREPRO ONLINE\" button_url_img_left=\"revatureonline.html\"]Learn leading-edge programming skills, access tutorials, and work on enterprise-level projects from anywhere, anytime.[/home_img_left_text_right][/home_img_txt_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_img_txt_container][home_text_left_img_right title_left=\"Coding Bootcamp\" img_right=\"119\" button_text=\"GO TO REVATUREPRO BOOTCAMP\" button_url=\"bootcamp.html\"]\n<p class=\"RevPro-Bootcamp-head\">Get accepted into our intensive, on-site coding bootcamp and work on leading-edge technology projects in a team-focused setting.</p>\n[/home_text_left_img_right][/home_img_txt_container][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Revaturepro', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-17 14:59:26', '2016-11-17 14:59:26', '', 5, 'http://localhost/rough/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
