(201, 1, '2016-12-05 14:15:25', '2016-12-05 14:15:25', '[vc_row][vc_column][about_section_hero_header title1=\"Not Just Forward-Thinking—Future-Thinking.\"]At Revature, we don\'t just see the future of business and technology—we\'re creating it[/about_section_hero_header][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][about_sub_nav][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][about_advance_and_tech_func main_title=\"Advancing Talent and Technologies.\" main_content=\"Revature empowers businesses around the globe with best-in-class talent and technologies. Our people work on the most innovative, challenging, and rewarding software development projects for leading Fortune 500 companies, government organizations, and top systems integrators. We offer three distinct advantages that help put our clients—and our people—ahead in the market: a one-of-a-kind talent delivery program, unparalleled expertise, and better control of your talent pipeline.\" left_img_1=\"1368\" right_title_1=\"Proprietary Talent Delivery Program\" right_content_1=\"Our unique training program lets us hire, develop, and deploy top talent well versed in leading-edge and next-gen technologies. Through continuous and intensive training focused on simulated, real-world issues, Revature associates are able to quickly integrate into your existing technology teams.\" right_img_2=\"1369\" left_title_2=\"Next-Gen Technologies Expertise\" left_content_2=\"We bring deep knowledge of and experience in all the latest enterprise-level technologies—and we’re constantly refining our program to incorporate the latest technology trends and enhancements in project delivery, including DevOps, SDET, and Cloud computing.\" left_img_3=\"1370\" right_title_3=\"Better Control of Your Talent Pipeline\" right_content_3=\"Because our talent delivery program can train people faster and more cost-effectively, we can help you ramp up quickly and integrate expert teams in large numbers right away.\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][principle_and_work_section main_title=\"Our Principles Defines Us and Our Work.\" main_content=\"AT Revature,we\'are about more than developing great talent and technology.The propelling force behind our work is to empower the next generation of innovation in technology.\" title_1=\"Our Mission\" content_1=\"To create the pathway where university graduates with diverse backgrounds can build the knowledge, skills and abilites to reach their potentials as technology professional and leverage those talents to contribute to the growth and sucess of our costomers\" title_2=\"Our Vision\" content_2=\"To create a world\'s most diverse and dynamic community of highly skilled and creative technology pioneers who are able to affect change and promote progress.\" title_3=\"Our Values\" content_3=\"We are group of people with wide ranging passions and aspirations,united by common values.Our communites is inclusive,diverse,respectful,caring and fun.Our people are curious,creative and original,inspiring and ambitious.\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][about_leadership_func main_title=\"Our Leadership Team\" main_content=\"Revature\'s executive leadership combines visionary thinking,seasoned expertise, and a passion for results.With extensive backgrounds in technology,academia,and businesses enterprises ranging from global corporations to start-ups,they brings the insight and expertise necessary to deliver secussful outcomes for our diverse range of clients.\" person_img_1=\"195\" person_title_1=\"Srikanth Ramachandran\" person_desig_1=\"Chief Executive Officer\" person_desc_1=\"Srikanth, Chief Executive Officer of Revature that he founded in 2014, drives the business strategy of the company and was responsible for the initial ideation of the Revature business model. Revature is at the forefront of innovation and talent development. Revature partners with top colleges and universities to provide students with no-risk pathways to high-value careers in coding and software development.\n\nPrior to Revature, Srikanth was the President of Multivision Inc., an IT consulting company. He has also served as a Director of IT at Columbia Research Group and a contract software engineer for the U.S. Navy.\n\nSrikanth holds a Bachelor’s Degree in Computer Science Engineering from Madras University, India. SmartCEO magazine selected him as a Future 50 CEO for the Washington, DC region. He was also a finalist for the Ernst and Young Entrepreneur of the Year award. He resides in Ashburn, VA.\n\" person_img_2=\"196\" person_title_2=\"Ashwin Bharath\" person_desig_2=\"Chief Operrating Officer\" person_desc_2=\"Ashwin serves as Revature’s Chief Operating Officer, having originally joined Multivision in 2004, as IT Manager and then as IT Director.\n\nAs COO, Ashwin is responsible for the daily operations of the company and ensures initiatives align with the company’s core values and culture. With extensive experience in domestic and international markets, Ashwin leads the development and implementation of products and services for our clients.\n\nPreviously, Ashwin held management positions with Satyam Computers. He has a Bachelor of Engineering, Electronics and Communications, from the Coimbatore Institute of Technology.\n\" person_img_3=\"200\" person_title_3=\"Joe Vacca\" person_desig_3=\"Chief Markeing Officer\" person_desc_3=\"Joe joined Revature as Chief Marketing Officer in July 2016, where he is responsible for building brand identity, sales development, marketing operations and digital strategy.\n\nWith more than 20 years’ experience, Joe was formerly the Chief Marketing Officer at Identity Guard. He also held executive positions with Intersections, EduCap and Wells Fargo. Joe brings deep experience in both direct-to-consumer and business-to-business marketing, and has worked with some of the largest companies in the U.S. including Bank of America, Costco, Citibank, Comcast and Capital One.\n\nJoe holds a Bachelor’s Degree in Marketing from Shepherd University and an MBA in Management from Frostburg State University\" person_img_4=\"198\" person_title_4=\"Justin Vianello\" person_desig_4=\"Chief Finacial Officer\" person_desc_4=\"Justin joined Revature as Chief Financial Officer in April 2016. As CFO, Justin works closely with the executives and private equity investors to develop and execute strategies for aggressive growth.\n\nPrior to Revature, Justin served as Global CFO at Manalto Limited, a publicly held technology company, as well as positions with Quantum Power Limited and Forex Management Systems, both located in Brisbane, Australia.\n\nJustin holds a degree in Business and Commerce from University of Port Elizabeth, and an Executive MBA, Business Administration and Management, from Bond University. He is a Chartered Accountant with the Institute of Chartered Accountants in Australia and South Africa.\n\" person_img_5=\"199\" person_title_5=\"Joe Mitchell\" person_desig_5=\"Executive Vice President, Academic Partnerships\" person_desc_5=\"Joe serves as Revature’s Executive Vice President of Academic Partnerships, where he is responsible for developing and managing Revature’s partnerships with colleges and universities.\n\nJoe has more than 15 years of experience in the education industry, leading technology and enterprise sales across North America and Europe. Prior to joining Revature in March 2016, Joe held senior leadership positions with Pearson and Blackboard, Inc., where he was responsible for developing partnerships to help universities scale their online operations.\n\nJoe graduated from University of Northampton with a degree in Information Systems and Business Administration, and started his early career as a software developer in London before co-founding an educational software and services company which led him to the U.S.\n\n\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][about_join_revature title=\"Join Revature and Move Ahead\" button_text=\"VISIT OUR CAREEERS PAGE \" button_url=\"#\"]\n\nWe are always looking for talented,innovative people to join our team.Check out exiciting careers opportunities at Revature.\n\n[/about_join_revature][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][about_student_and_business left_title=\"RevaturePro for Students\" left_content=\"Learn how you can fast-track your carrer and work on some of the most innivative, challenging,and rewarding technology for leading companies.\" left_btn_url=\"revaturepro\" left_btn_txt=\"LEARN MORE\" right_title=\"RevaturePro for Business\" right_content=\"Learn how we train people faster and more cost-effectively providing qualified technology talent that can contribute to your business right away.\" right_btn_url=\"acamedic-partners\" right_btn_txt=\"LEARN MORE\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_contact_us btn_txt=\"CONTACT US\" btn_url=\"../contact-us\"]\n\nReady to Advance?\n\n[/home_contact_us][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Revature', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-05 14:15:25', '2016-12-05 14:15:25', '', 2, 'http://localhost/rough/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
