(241, 1, '2016-12-06 14:31:10', '2016-12-06 14:31:10', '[vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_header bg_image=\"428\" title=\"RevaturePro Bootcamp\" img_logo=\"1218\"]Get intensive training and become certified in the latest enterprise-level, next-gen, and niche technologies for <strong>free</strong>—then get hired by Revature when you’re done.[/bootcamp_header][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][online_log_in_banner btn_url=\"#apply\" btn_txt=\"APPLY TODAY\"]Ready to take the next step to fast-track your career?[/online_log_in_banner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][online_two_column_txt_img title=\"Get Certified in Leading-Edge Technologies—on Us.\" img_url=\"244\"]\n<p class=\"rev-bootcamp-p\">Most coding bootcamps are expensive to attend and, beyond getting certified, offer no guarantee of a job once you’ve finished the program\nRevaturePro’s coding bootcamps break that mold.\n\n<p class=\"rev-bootcamp-p\">Our bootcamps are <b>free</b> to accepted applicants and include all of the following:</p>\n\n<ul class=\"padding-left-20\">\n 	<li class=\"li-font-18\">A 12-week immersive, industry-aligned coding program</li>\n 	<li class=\"li-font-18\">A $250 travel allowance to attend the bootcamp</li>\n 	<li class=\"li-font-18\">12 weeks of accommodation and a living stipend</li>\n 	<li class=\"li-font-18\">All books and training materials</li>\n 	<li class=\"li-font-18\">Professional certification (Microsoft, Oracle, etc.)</li>\n 	<li class=\"li-font-18\">Dedicated industry mentors to ensure your success during bootcamp and your first two years of employment</li>\n 	<li class=\"li-font-18\">A unique ePortfolio that showcases your projects, experience, accomplishments, and certifications</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"rev-bootcamp-p\">Even better, once you’ve successfully completed our bootcamp, Revature will hire you as a full-time software development professional.</p>\n[/online_two_column_txt_img][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_quick_facts title_1=\"The Coding Bootcamp That Invests in You!\" content_1=\"Beyond providing free training, certification, and accommodations—as well as guaranteed employment once you’ve successfully completed our program—there are three key differentiators that make the RevaturePro Bootcamp stand out.\" title_2=\"Enterprise Project–Driven\" content_2=\"The projects you work on are not theoretical. They are enterprise-level projects that have application in real-world business and technology. As you learn and build your skills, you’re gaining actual industry experience.\" title_3=\"Highly Customized Program\" content_3=\"Your program can be designed based on the skills you want to learn and the projects you want to work on. It can also be customized to where you want to live and work, since our bootcamps are offered at Revature offices across the country, as well as on the campuses of our partner universities.\" title_4=\"One-on-One Attention\" content_4=\"You’ll have a mentor to help and advise you throughout the bootcamp, as well as the first two years of employment. We truly invest in your success, providing in-depth, comprehensive instruction and personal attention, helping to ensure you’ll rock your tech career.\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_six_steps title_1=\"How It Works.\" content_1=\"We’re always on the lookout for people with talent and drive to attend our bootcamps and become part of our Revature team. The steps below outline how our program works.\" title_2=\"Apply for Bootcamp\" content_2=\"Our online application process is simple and fast. Also, if you’ve shown aptitude through the RevaturePro online program, we may reach out to you and offer admission to our bootcamp program.\" img_2=\"225\" title_3=\"Have an Interview\" content_3=\"If your application is accepted, you’ll be interviewed via phone or Skype. Here, we’ll talk to you more in depth about what skills you want to learn, the certification you want, and your career goals.\" img_3=\"245\" title_4=\"Customize Your Program\" content_4=\"Choose from hundreds of enterprise-level, next-gen, and niche technology programming skills and dozens of certification programs to create a course of study based on the projects you want to work on.\" img_4=\"246\" title_5=\"Attend Bootcamp\" content_5=\"We’ll bring you to one of our bootcamps throughout the country, where you’ll go through an intensive and customized 12-week program, learning the skills and working on projects that set you on your career path.\" img_5=\"247\" title_6=\"Get Certified\" content_6=\"Not only do we pay for your certification in the technology you want, we ensure that you receive that technology’s highest certification. Additionally, you’ll be industry certified as a Revature Certified Professional.\" img_6=\"213\" title_7=\"Get Hired\" content_7=\"After you’ve successfully completing bootcamp, you’ll be hired as a Revature Professional and join our talented team, working on leading-edge technologies for many of the most innovative companies in the world.\" img_7=\"230\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_testimonial title=\"What Students Are Saying About Us.\" content_1=\"I know I wouldn\'t have gotten this position if it hadn\'t been for Revature.\" name_1=\"Yasmine Sadid\" school_1=\"Kent State University (now working at Capital One)\" content_2=\"Revature truly has been in a once in a lifetime opportunity. During my time here I have been learning the stack from front to back, particularly in Java as well as automation frameworks like Cucumber which I have no doubt will prove invaluable at any company.\" name_2=\"Braden Ripple\" school_2=\"Utah State (now working as a software engineer for Walmart)\" content_3=\"The industry is evolving quickly and my biggest fear was I wasn’t going to be able to get a job. Revature came through…all I needed was that one job.\" name_3=\"Christopher Kurz\" school_3=\"B.A. in English from UCLA\" content_4=\"We work on cool stuff. College was great but the curriculum was set in stone, Revature teaches you the newer technologies such as Hibernate.\" name_4=\"Kevin Jones\" school_4=\"Oregon State\" content_5=\"If I hadn’t done this program, I think I would still be searching for a development job or possibly changing my career field. I have come here to perfect this knowledge, this technology and I’ve done it!\" name_5=\"RaVaughn Green\" school_5=\"University of Maryland\" content_6=\"The program has been amazing in taking me from a non-Computer Science background to a marketable IT professional.\" name_6=\"Omari Maxwell\" school_6=\"University of Pennsylania\" content_7=\"Part of the programming is learning how to interview and talk with people, which is challenging for most computer programmers. Revature provides a place to learn how to speak with technologists and create a rapport.\" name_7=\"Frank Emmert\" school_7=\"Purdue University\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_apply_form confirm_title=\"Thank You\" confirm_content=\"Thank you for your interest in the RevaturePro program. We\'ll be in touch with you soon.\" title=\"Ready to Launch Your Tech Career into Hyperdrive?\" title_1=\"\" content_1=\"\" link_text_1=\"\" link_url_1=\"\" title_2=\"\" content_2=\"\" link_text_2=\"\" link_url_2=\"\" form_content=\"Apply to our RevaturePro Bootcamp program today!\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_bottom_two_column title_1=\"RevaturePro Online.\" content_1=\"Gain experience in the latest enterprise-level programming skills by working on real-world project scenarios through our free online program.\" link_text_1=\"GO TO REVATUREPRO ONLINE\" link_url_1=\"revatureonline.html\" title_2=\"About Revature\" content_2=\"We at Revature are at the forefront of talent and technology solutions, empowering students, universities, and businesses to move forward, faster.\" link_text_2=\"LEARN MORE\" link_url_2=\"index.html\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_advance title=\"Ready to Advance?\" button_text=\"CONTACT US\" button_url=\"contactus.html?bootcamp\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Bootcamp', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'coding-bootcamp', '', '', '2017-04-18 13:42:37', '2017-04-18 13:42:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/rough/?page_id=241', 0, 'page', '', 0),
