(260, 1, '2016-12-12 13:54:53', '2016-12-12 13:54:53', '[vc_row][vc_column][home_video_header video_src=\"1180\"]Advancing Talent and Technologies.[/home_video_header][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_what_we_do title=\"What We Do\" button_text=\"LEARN MORE ABOUT US\" button_url=\"about-revature\"]Revature makes leading-edge, next-gen, and niche technologies work for businesses around the globe to put them out in front of their competition. At the heart of our solutions is our unique talent development and delivery platform, which drives success for our many Fortune 500 and technology industry clients.[/home_what_we_do][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text][recent] [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_img_txt_container][home_img_txt_header title=\"Advance Faster and Get Farther Ahead.\" logo_img=\"167\" button_text=\"LEARN MORE ABOUT REVATUREPRO\" button_url=\"../revaturepro\"]RevaturePro is about propelling technology talent–as well as academic institutions and businesses–forward faster and more efficiently than ever before. Ready to accelerate your path to success?[/home_img_txt_header][home_img_left_text_right title_img_left=\"Online Program\" content_img_left=\"\n\n\" logo_img_img_left=\"118\" button_text_img_left=\"GO TO REVATUREPRO ONLINE\" button_url_img_left=\"../online\"]Gain experience in the latest enterprise-level programming skills by working on real-world project scenarios through our free online program.[/home_img_left_text_right][home_text_left_img_right title_left=\"Coding Bootcamp\" content_left=\"\n\n\" img_right=\"237\" button_text=\"GO TO REVATURE BOOTCAMP\" button_url=\"../revaturepro\"]Get the experience you need fast by learning leading-edge programming skills in our intensive 12-week program.[/home_text_left_img_right][home_img_left_text_right title_img_left=\"Colleges and Universities\" logo_img_img_left=\"236\" button_text_img_left=\"GO TO ACADEMIC PARTNERSHIPS\" button_url_img_left=\