nologists and create a rapport.\" name_7=\"Frank Emmert\" school_7=\"Purdue University\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_contact_us btn_txt=\"CONTACT US\" btn_url=\"../contact-us\"]Ready to Advance?[/home_contact_us][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Index', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '183-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-12 13:54:53', '2016-12-12 13:54:53', '', 183, 'http://localhost/rough/183-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
