ill I need a parking pass for the apartment and the office? \"]Parking at Revature is available in the adjacent garage at no cost. Depending on what complex you will be living in, you may need a parking permit, which can be obtained at the leasing office.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Do I need to bring furniture, kitchenware and appliances, and bedding? \"]Revature provides a completely furnished apartment including twin-sized beds, dressers, table, chairs, kitchen appliances, dishes, utensils, pots and pans, as well as bedding. You are more than welcome to bring your own bedding should you choose to do so. You should bring your own laundry detergent and toiletries / personal hygiene items as well as your own food.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Can I bring my pets?\"]Unfortunately, we have a “No Pets” policy.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Will I have to clean the apartment?\"]Revature provides a cleaning service every other week, however, you are expected to maintain a clean and healthy environment.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Are there televisions in the apartments?\"]Televisions and game consoles are neither provided nor allowed.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Can I have guests come and stay?\"]No, it is strictly prohibited to have non- Revature Associates staying at the apartments. There are multiple hotels conveniently located throughout the area.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Who should I contact for housing supplies and maintenance issues? \"]Email <a href=\"mailto:housing@revature.com\">housing@revature.com</a> to request paper towels, toilet tissue, dish-washing liquid, trash bags and light bulbs.\n\nEmail <a href=\"mailto:maintenance@revature.com\">maintenance@revature.com</a> for any maintenance issues you encounter. Do not attempt any repairs yourself. We will then submit a work order to the maintenance personnel. They usually respond within 24 - 48 hours.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"What mailing address should I use?\"]All mail should be addressed as follows:\n\nYour Name\nc/o Revature\n11730 Plaza America Drive\n2<sup>nd</sup> Floor\nReston, VA 20190[/revaturepro_faq_item][/revaturepro_faq_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][housing_header_hero title=\"Corporate Housing\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Housing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '615-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-27 10:55:06', '2017-03-27 10:55:06', '', 615, 'http://localhost/rough/615-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
