_row][vc_column][home_testimonial title=\"What Students Are Saying About Us.\" content_1=\"I know I wouldn\'t have gotten this position if it hadn\'t been for Revature.\" name_1=\"Yasmine Sadid\" school_1=\"Kent State University (now working at Capital One)\" content_2=\"Revature truly has been in a once in a lifetime opportunity. During my time here I have been learning the stack from front to back, particularly in Java as well as automation frameworks like Cucumber which I have no doubt will prove invaluable at any company.\" name_2=\"Braden Ripple\" school_2=\"Utah State (now working as a software engineer for Walmart)\" content_3=\"The industry is evolving quickly and my biggest fear was I wasn’t going to be able to get a job. Revature came through…all I needed was that one job.\" name_3=\"Christopher Kurz\" school_3=\"B.A. in English from UCLA\" content_4=\"We work on cool stuff. College was great but the curriculum was set in stone, Revature teaches you the newer technologies such as Hibernate.\" name_4=\"Kevin Jones\" school_4=\"Oregon State\" content_5=\"If I hadn’t done this program, I think I would still be searching for a development job or possibly changing my career field. I have come here to perfect this knowledge, this technology and I’ve done it!\" content_8=\"Part of the programming is learning how to interview and talk with people, which is challenging for most computer programmers. Revature provides a place to learn how to speak with technologists and create a rapport.\" name_8=\"Frank Emmert\" school_8=\"Purdue Universitys\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_contact_us btn_txt=\"CONTACT US\" btn_url=\"../contact-us\"]Ready to Advance?[/home_contact_us][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Index', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '183-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-17 09:40:54', '2017-04-17 09:40:54', '', 183, 'http://localhost/rough/blog/2017/04/17/183-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
