(822, 1, '2017-04-17 16:29:53', '2017-04-17 16:29:53', '[vc_row][vc_column][corporate_header title=\"The Next Generation of Technology Talent\" btn_txt=\"LEARN MORE\" btn_url=\"/contact-us?corporate\"]Revature completely redefines how companies find, build, retain and grow their future technology talent.[/corporate_header][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][corporate_sub_nav][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][corporate_horizontal_steps title=\"Changing The Way The World Hires\" img_1=\"1349\" title_1=\"Recruit\" txt_1=\"We’re selective about our technology talent, recruiting the top 1% from colleges and universities throughout the country.\" title_2=\"Develop\" txt_2=\"Through our intensive bootcamps and online programs, we turn entry-level coders into world-class software engineers.\" title_3=\"Deploy\" txt_3=\"We deliver job-ready technology talent fast, cutting down onboarding time so you can focus on your project’s success.\" title_4=\"Hire\" txt_4=\"Our talent seamlessly integrates with existing technology teams so well that they end up being hired by clients.\" img_2=\"1350\" img_3=\"1351\" img_4=\"1352\"]Our proprietary talent development and delivery program takes the unpredictability out of securing the right people while eliminating wasted efforts, time and money in the process.[/corporate_horizontal_steps][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][corporate_benefits_orange_header title=\"The Benefits of Partnering with Revature\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][corporate_benefits_orange_items title_1=\"Up-to-Speed on In-Demand Technologies\" content_1=\"Revature eliminates the “skills gap” by putting our people through intensive and continuous training in the latest in-demand, enterprise-level and next-gen technologies—so you don’t have to.\" title_2=\"Custom Trained for Your Environment\" content_2=\"We create exclusive talent pools that are custom trained to meet your technology needs and business goals, as well as work with you to enhance your existing talent and provide resources with hard-to-find skills.\" title_3=\"Predictable Talent Acquisition Model\" content_3=\"Because our talent has been specifically trained for your systems and environment, vetted and proven, the cost of “wrong hires” has been taken out of the mix—with SLAs guaranteed.\" title_4=\"Increased Efficiency and Productivity\" content_4=\"Our talented professionals come to you well versed in the leading-edge skills you need, so you can ramp up quickly and integrate experienced teams in large numbers right away—increasing productivity by up to 80%.\" title_5=\"Cost-Effective Solutions Delivery\" content_5=\"Our model eliminates your costs for recruiting, training and retaining skilled technology talent. We also provide nationwide deployment and relocation, removing the burden from your HR department.\" title_6=\"Reduced Attrition of Resources\" content_6=\"Our skilled professionals are contracted to you and committed to the success of your organization for the entire duration of your project, with no drop off of resources and no time or money lost due to attrition.\" icon_1=\"216\" icon_2=\"217\" icon_3=\"218\" icon_4=\"219\" icon_5=\"220\" icon_6=\"221\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][corporate_quick_facts title=\"Results Where It Counts.\" title_1=\"70%\" title_2=\"3 times\" content_2=\"Improvement in hiring high performing talent.\" title_3=\"4 times\" content_3=\"Less attrition than the industry average.\" header_1=\"70%\" header_2=\"3 times\" header_3=\"4 times\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_faq_marketo_container title=\"marketo container\" sub_title=\"aasd\" btn_txt=\"apply now\"][/revaturepro_faq_marketo_container][revaturepro_faq_container title=\"Have Questions? We Have Answers.\" sub_title=\"Have a Specific Question? \" btn_txt=\"CONTACT US\" btn_url=\"../contact-us\"][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Why is there a 2 year contract?\"]Because.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"What is Revature?\"]Revature is the best company in the world[/revaturepro_faq_item][/revaturepro_faq_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][corporate_quote title=\"Need Workforce Modernization?\" btn_txt=\"LEARN MORE\" btn_url=\"../work-force\" quote=\"A decade ago the half life of a Software Engineer was 2.5 years. Imagine how short it is in today’s world of changing technology.\"]In addition to providing companies with the best technology talent to help move their businesses forward, Revature offers programs—both online and on-site—to help bring your existing workforce up to speed on the latest leading-edge, next-gen and niche technologies. Contact us to learn how we can give your technology professionals the winning edge.[/corporate_quote][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][corporate_pipeline title=\"End to End Managed Technical Recruiting\" btn_txt=\"LEARN MORE\" btn_url=\"../technical-recruting\"]Revature can manage all aspects of your talent recruitment and development process, allowing you to focus on your core business. Through our corporate-sponsored university coding bootcamps, we’re able to recruit the best talent, custom-train them in the languages and skills that matter to your organization, and then deploy them directly into your teams across the country, ready to hit the ground running.[/corporate_pipeline][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_faq_container title=\"Have Questions? We Have Answers.\" sub_title=\"Have a Specific Question? \" btn_txt=\"CONTACT US\" btn_url=\"../contact-us\"][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"How are you different from technology staffing companies?\"]Revature upends the traditional tech-staffing model. Our talent development program enables us to recruit, train and place experienced software developers to meet your specific software development needs and targeted goals.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"How are you different from coding bootcamps?\"]Quite simply, we’ve flipped the traditional coding bootcamp model. While they rely on student enrollment to generate income, we invest in our associates, providing them with the latest enterprise-level training in the software technologies you need. Because Revature pays for the training, we are highly selective with our recruitment. Our incentive is providing you with qualified, experienced software developers.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Is it more expensive than a direct hire?\"]Not at all—in fact, our partners generally see a 20% savings compared to the costs they pay for recruiting, training and mis-hiring that come with direct employment.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Can I request developers with specific skills?\"]Absolutely. Revature delivers custom-tailored and cost-effective talent skilled in advanced technologies that meet your business needs. That is the cornerstone of our business.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"How does your business work with our internal recruiting team?\"]Revature works as a complement to your internal team. We work closely with your team to identify your needs and provide you with predictable, custom-trained technology talent exactly when and where you need it.[/revaturepro_faq_item][/revaturepro_faq_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][online_bottom_two_column left_title=\"RevaturePro for Students\" left_content=\"Learn how you can fast-track your career and work on some of the most innovative, challenging and rewarding technology for leading companies.\" left_btn_txt=\"LEARN MORE\" left_btn_url=\"../revaturepro\" right_title=\"RevaturePro for Academic Institutions\" right_content=\"Learn how we can help colleges and universities provide no-risk pathways to careers in technology for their students and graduates.\" right_btn_txt=\"LEARN MORE\" right_btn_url=\"../academic-partners\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Corporate Partners', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '189-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-17 16:29:53', '2017-04-17 16:29:53', '', 189, 'http://localhost/rough/blog/2017/04/17/189-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
