mp; Easy\" content_2=\"Fill out an online registration form, take a quick basic skills test, and select a technical track—all in 15 minutes or less.\" img_2=\"225\" title_3=\"Start Working\" content_3=\"Whether online or in one of our bootcamps, you jump into real-world project scenarios right away, learning as you go through tutorials and mentor guidance.\" img_3=\"224\" title_4=\"Connect with a Mentor\" content_4=\"Mentorship is unique to the RevaturePro experience, both online and in our bootcamps. You’ll receive one-on-one guidance and instruction with an industry-experienced mentor throughout your program.\" img_4=\"227\" title_5=\"Get Certified\" content_5=\"Earn certifications during and upon completion of your program that highlight not only your technical abilities, but your work/project experience.\" img_5=\"228\" title_6=\"Show Off Your Skills\" content_6=\"Build an online portfolio that showcases every element of your program: skills, projects, application screenshots, sample code, certifications, ratings, and reviews.\" img_6=\"229\" title_7=\"Get Hired\" content_7=\"Start working for Revature as a software development professional, working on innovative and leading-edge projects for one of our many corporate partners.\" img_7=\"230\" id=\"howItWorks\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_two_column_container][revaturepro_two_column_header title=\"Two Ways to Move Ahead.\"]RevaturePro gives you two routes to the front of the technology talent market—online and in person. Either way, we put you in a position to win.[/revaturepro_two_column_header][revaturepro_two_column_img_left img=\"204\" title=\"Online Program\" btn_txt=\"GO TO REVATUREPRO ONLINE\" btn_url=\"../online\"]Learn leading-edge programming skills, access tutorials, and work on enterprise-level projects from anywhere, anytime.[/revaturepro_two_column_img_left][revaturepro_two_column_img_right img=\"232\" title=\"Coding Bootcamp\" btn_txt=\"GO TO REVATUREPRO BOOTCAMP\" btn_url=\"coding-bootcamp\"]Get accepted into our intensive, on-site coding bootcamp and work on leading-edge technology projects in a team-focused setting.[/revaturepro_two_column_img_right][/revaturepro_two_column_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_get_it_going title=\"Ready to Get IT Going with RevaturePro?\" btn_txt_1=\"SIGN UP FOR ONLINE TRAINING\" btn_url_1=\"https://app.revature.com/signup\" btn_txt_2=\"APPLY TO OUR BOOTCAMP\" btn_url_2=\"../bootcamp#apply\"]See how we can fast-track your technology career.[/revaturepro_get_it_going][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_faq_container title=\"Still Have Questions? We\'ve Got Answers!\" sub_title=\"Have a Specific Question?\" btn_txt=\"CONTACT US\" btn_url=\"../contact-us\"][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"What makes Revature unique?\"]Revature’s proprietary training and talent delivery platform makes us unique in the industry. Our platform ensures that the talent we provide has the job-ready, enterprise-level skills in leading-edge and niche technologies that today’s companies need right now.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"What programs does Revature offer?\"]Revature offers both an online program and an in-person coding bootcamp program. There are no qualifications necessary to enroll in the online program—just a can-do attitude and a desire to great work in the technology sector. Applicants to our coding bootcamps are required to take a skills test and undergo a short interview. Both programs are free to applicants.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Can I contact a recruiter directly about employment opportunities?\"]Yes. You can reach a recruiter directly by calling the recruitment team’s number at (703) 570-8282.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Should I apply for the online program or the residential coding bootcamp?\"]It depends. Anyone can apply to our online program—and it offers the ability to gain the skills and certifications you need from practically anywhere. However, if you already have some coding experience and wish to gain job-ready skills and certifications—as well as a guaranteed job in technology once you’ve successfully completed the program—then we suggest you apply to our coding bootcamp.[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"Can I join the coding bootcamp if I have no coding experience?\"]While anyone can apply, the coding bootcamp is very immersive and intensive. A background in coding is essential to successfully completing the program. If you have no coding experience, we suggest you enroll in our free online program first. Once you’ve completed that, we’d love to have you apply for one of our coding bootcamps.[/revaturepro_faq_item][/revaturepro_faq_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_two_column_callout title=\"RevaturePro for Academic Institutions\" btn_txt=\"LEARN MORE\" btn_url=\"../academic-partners\"]Learn how we can help you provide no-risk pathways to careers in technology for your students and graduates.[/revaturepro_two_column_callout][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][revaturepro_faq_container][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"as\"]asd[/revaturepro_faq_item][revaturepro_faq_item title=\"amar\"]amar singh[/revaturepro_faq_item][/revaturepro_faq_container][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Join Our Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '813-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-18 11:41:18', '2017-04-18 11:41:18', '', 813, 'http://localhost/rough/blog/2017/04/18/813-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
