gy path from a broad range of offerings, as well as learn and work on projects from anywhere.\" icon_6=\"826\" title_6=\"Start your technology career faster\" content_6=\"Our intensive program gives you the leading-edge, enterprise-level technology skills businesses need in as little as 12 weeks. Best of all, when you successfully complete the program, we’ll hire you as a Revature software development professional!\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_quick_facts title_1=\"The Coding Company That Invests in You!\" content_1=\"Beyond providing free training, certification, and accommodations—as well as guaranteed employment once you’ve successfully completed our program—there are three key differentiators that make Revature stand out.\" title_2=\"Enterprise Project–Driven\" content_2=\"The projects you work on are not theoretical. They are enterprise-level projects that have application in real-world business and technology. As you learn and build your skills, you’re gaining actual industry experience.\" title_3=\"Highly Customized Program\" content_3=\"Our program is designed based on the skills you want to learn and the projects our clients need, allowing you to work on projects that they have identified as vital to their organization. More than that, we prepare you to work in the “real world” with communication, team work and leadership training.\" title_4=\"One-on-One Attention\" content_4=\"You’ll have a mentor to help and advise you throughout the our program, as well as the first two years of employment. We truly invest in your success, providing in-depth, comprehensive instruction and personal attention, helping to ensure you’ll rock your tech career.\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_six_steps title_1=\"How It Works.\" content_1=\"We’re always on the lookout for people with talent and drive to attend our training and become part of our Revature team. The steps below outline how our program works.\" title_2=\"Apply\" content_2=\"Our online application process is simple and fast. Also, if you’ve shown aptitude through the RevaturePro online program, we may reach out to you and offer admission to our program.\" img_2=\"225\" title_3=\"Have an Interview\" content_3=\"If your application is accepted, you’ll be interviewed via phone or Skype. Here, we’ll talk to you more in depth about what skills you want to learn, the certifications you want, and your career goals.\" img_3=\"245\" title_4=\"Show Your Skills\" content_4=\"As the home of “hard core coding” we want the best and brightest. Show us your skills using our technology screening interview.\" img_4=\"246\" title_5=\"Attend Training\" content_5=\"We’ll bring you to one of our offices throughout the country, where you’ll go through an intensive and customized 12-week program, learning the skills and working on projects that set you on your career path.\" img_5=\"247\" title_6=\"Get Certified\" content_6=\"Not only do we pay for your certification in the technology you want, we ensure that you receive that technology’s highest certification. Additionally, you’ll be industry certified as a Revature Certified Software Engineer.\" img_6=\"213\" title_7=\"Start Your Career\" content_7=\"After you’ve successfully completing bootcamp, you’ll be hired as a Revature Professional and join our talented team, working on leading-edge technologies for many of the most innovative companies in the world.\" img_7=\"230\" id=\"howItWorks\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][home_testimonial title=\"What Associates Are Saying About Us.\" content_1=\"I know I wouldn\'t have gotten this position if it hadn\'t been for Revature.\" name_1=\"Yasmine Sadid\" school_1=\"Kent State University (now working at Capital One)\" content_2=\"Revature truly has been in a once in a lifetime opportunity. During my time here I have been learning the stack from front to back, particularly in Java as well as automation frameworks like Cucumber which I have no doubt will prove invaluable at any company.\" name_2=\"Braden Ripple\" school_2=\"Utah State (now working as a software engineer for Walmart)\" content_3=\"The industry is evolving quickly and my biggest fear was I wasn’t going to be able to get a job. Revature came through…all I needed was that one job.\" name_3=\"Christopher Kurz\" school_3=\"B.A. in English from UCLA\" content_4=\"We work on cool stuff. College was great but the curriculum was set in stone, Revature teaches you the newer technologies such as Hibernate.\" name_4=\"Kevin Jones\" school_4=\"Oregon State\" content_5=\"If I hadn’t done this program, I think I would still be searching for a development job or possibly changing my career field. I have come here to perfect this knowledge, this technology and I’ve done it!\" name_5=\"RaVaughn Green\" school_5=\"University of Maryland\" content_6=\"The program has been amazing in taking me from a non-Computer Science background to a marketable IT professional.\" name_6=\"Omari Maxwell\" school_6=\"University of Pennsylania\" content_7=\"Part of the programming is learning how to interview and talk with people, which is challenging for most computer programmers. Revature provides a place to learn how to speak with technologists and create a rapport.\" name_7=\"Frank Emmert\" school_7=\"Purdue University\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][bootcamp_without_apply_form title=\"Ready to Launch Your Tech Career into Hyperdrive?\" form_content=\"Apply to our RevaturePro Bootcamp program today!\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Join Our Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '813-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-18 15:46:29', '2017-04-18 15:46:29', '', 813, 'http://localhost/rough/blog/2017/04/18/813-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
